message.name: INF_XRV_RELEASED_RECORD_WITH_SAME_EFFECTIVE_DATE_EXISTS
message.locale: A Released mapping already exists with an effective date of %1d. If you proceed, this existing mapping will be superseded by your new mapping. Are you sure you want to release this mapping?

message.name: INF_XRV_RELEASED_RECORD_WITH_EARLIER_EFFECTIVE_DATE_EXISTS
message.locale: Released mappings already exist with effective dates before that of your new mapping. If you proceed, your new mapping will supersede the existing mappings from %1d. Are you sure you want to release this mapping?

message.name: INF_XRV_RELEASED_RECORD_WITH_LATER_EFFECTIVE_DATE_EXISTS
message.locale: Released mappings already exist with effective dates that are after your new mapping. If you proceed, your new mapping will only be active until the nearest effective date. Are you sure you want to release this mapping?
